{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "suluh-career-roadmap-api-v1",
    "name": "Suluh Career Roadmap API",
    "description": "Koleksi endpoint API untuk platform Suluh Career Roadmap.\n\n## Autentikasi\nAPI ini menggunakan tiga metode autentikasi:\n1. **Basic Auth** — untuk endpoint `POST /auth/login`\n2. **JWT Bearer Token** — untuk endpoint yang memerlukan login user\n3. **API Key (X-API-KEY)** — untuk endpoint data publik & riset institusi\n\n## Base URL\n`{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n## Cara Penggunaan\n1. Jalankan `POST Register` terlebih dahulu\n2. Jalankan `POST Login` — salin token ke variabel `{{jwt_token}}`\n3. Gunakan endpoint lain dengan token tersebut",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "SULUH-RESEARCH-KEY-2026",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Autentikasi (Auth)",
      "description": "Endpoint untuk registrasi, login, dan logout.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Daftar Akun Baru)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n  \"email\": \"budi@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mendaftarkan pengguna baru. Mengembalikan JWT token secara langsung.\n\n**Method:** POST (Tidak memerlukan autentikasi)\n\n**Request Body:**\n- `name` (required) — Nama lengkap\n- `email` (required) — Email unik\n- `password` (required, min:8) — Kata sandi\n- `password_confirmation` (required) — Konfirmasi kata sandi\n\n**Response 201:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Registrasi berhasil.\",\n  \"user\": { ... },\n  \"token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1Qi...\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 - Registrasi Berhasil",
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Registrasi berhasil.\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n    \"email\": \"budi@example.com\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-06-06T12:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 - Email Sudah Terdaftar",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Email sudah terdaftar.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"email\": [\"Email ini sudah digunakan.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Basic Auth → JWT Token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Basic {{basic_auth_base64}}",
                "description": "Format: Base64(email:password). Contoh untuk budi@example.com:password123 → Basic YnVkaUBleGFtcGxlLmNvbTpwYXNzd29yZDEyMw=="
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                {"key": "username", "value": "budi@example.com"},
                {"key": "password", "value": "password123"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Login menggunakan **HTTP Basic Auth** (email & password di-encode Base64 di header Authorization).\n\nSetelah login berhasil, salin nilai `token` dari response dan set ke variable `{{jwt_token}}`.\n\n**Catatan:** Di Postman, gunakan tab 'Authorization' → pilih 'Basic Auth', isi Username & Password.\n\n**Response 200:**\n```json\n{\n  \"message\": \"Login berhasil.\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1Qi...\",\n  \"token_type\": \"bearer\",\n  \"expires_in\": 3600\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Login Berhasil",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Login berhasil.\",\n  \"user\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n    \"email\": \"budi@example.com\"\n  },\n  \"token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJodHRwOi8vbG9jYWxob3N0OjgwMDAvYXBpL3YxL2F1dGgvbG9naW4iLCJpYXQiOjE3NDkxMjM2MDB9...\",\n  \"token_type\": \"bearer\",\n  \"expires_in\": 3600\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "401 - Kredensial Salah",
              "status": "Unauthorized",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Email atau kata sandi tidak cocok.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Membatalkan (invalidate) JWT token yang sedang aktif. Token tidak bisa digunakan lagi setelah ini.\n\n**Memerlukan:** `Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}`"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Logout Berhasil",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Logout berhasil.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Profil Pengguna (User Profile)",
      "description": "Endpoint untuk membaca dan mengubah profil pengguna yang sedang login.\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT Token",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Profil Saya",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/user/profile",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "user", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil data profil pengguna yang sedang login beserta karir yang dipilih."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Data Profil",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"profile\": {\n    \"name\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n    \"email\": \"budi@example.com\",\n    \"age_range\": \"22-25\",\n    \"education_level\": \"S1\",\n    \"work_experience\": \"0-1 tahun\",\n    \"current_career\": {\n      \"id\": 3,\n      \"name\": \"Data Scientist\",\n      \"riasec_code\": \"IAS\"\n    },\n    \"personality_scores\": null\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "PUT Update Profil",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/user/profile",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "user", "profile"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Budi Santoso Updated\",\n  \"age_range\": \"22-25\",\n  \"education_level\": \"S1\",\n  \"work_experience\": \"1-3 tahun\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mengubah data profil. Semua field bersifat `sometimes` (opsional)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Profil Diperbarui",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Profil diperbarui.\",\n  \"profile\": {\n    \"name\": \"Budi Santoso Updated\",\n    \"email\": \"budi@example.com\",\n    \"age_range\": \"22-25\",\n    \"education_level\": \"S1\",\n    \"work_experience\": \"1-3 tahun\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Asesmen Kepribadian (Assessment)",
      "description": "Endpoint untuk mengsubmit jawaban tes RIASEC & Big Five.\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT Token",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Submit Jawaban Asesmen",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/assessment/submit",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "assessment", "submit"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"answers\": {\n    \"1\": 8,\n    \"2\": 6,\n    \"3\": \"a\",\n    \"4\": 7,\n    \"5\": 9\n  }\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mengirim jawaban asesmen. Sistem akan menghitung skor RIASEC & Big Five, lalu merekomendasikan karir yang cocok menggunakan algoritma Euclidean Distance.\n\n**Body:** `answers` adalah object di mana key = ID soal dan value = jawaban (integer 1-10 untuk scale, 'a'/'b'/'c'/'d' untuk pilihan ganda)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Asesmen Berhasil Disubmit",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Asesmen berhasil disubmit.\",\n  \"result\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"riasec\": {\n      \"R\": 45, \"I\": 78, \"A\": 60, \"S\": 55, \"E\": 40, \"C\": 50\n    },\n    \"big_five\": {\n      \"openness\": 75, \"conscientiousness\": 68, \"extraversion\": 42,\n      \"agreeableness\": 70, \"neuroticism\": 30\n    },\n    \"top_careers\": [\n      {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"Data Scientist\", \"match_score\": 0.92},\n      {\"id\": 7, \"name\": \"Machine Learning Engineer\", \"match_score\": 0.88}\n    ]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Roadmap & Progres Skill",
      "description": "Endpoint untuk melihat roadmap karir dan mengupdate status belajar skill.\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT Token",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Roadmap Karir Saat Ini",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/roadmap/current",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "roadmap", "current"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil roadmap karir pengguna yang sedang aktif, dikelompokkan per level (beginner, intermediate, advanced)."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Data Roadmap",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"career\": {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"Data Scientist\", \"riasec_code\": \"IAS\"},\n  \"stages\": [\n    {\n      \"level\": \"beginner\",\n      \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n      \"skill_count\": 5,\n      \"completed\": 3,\n      \"skills\": [\n        {\"skill_id\": 1, \"name\": \"Python Dasar\", \"status\": \"done\"},\n        {\"skill_id\": 2, \"name\": \"Statistik Deskriptif\", \"status\": \"done\"},\n        {\"skill_id\": 3, \"name\": \"Pandas & NumPy\", \"status\": \"in_progress\"}\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"level\": \"intermediate\",\n      \"status\": \"not_started\",\n      \"skill_count\": 4,\n      \"completed\": 0,\n      \"skills\": []\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 - Belum Memilih Karir",
              "status": "Not Found",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Belum memilih karir.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "PATCH Update Status Skill",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/progress/update",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "progress", "update"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"skill_id\": 1,\n  \"status\": \"done\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mengubah status belajar sebuah skill. Status yang tersedia: `not_started`, `learning`, `in_progress`, `done`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Status Diperbarui",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Status skill diperbarui.\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 - Validasi Gagal",
              "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
              "code": 422,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"The status field must be one of not_started, learning, in_progress, done.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"status\": [\"The status field must be one of not_started, learning, in_progress, done.\"]\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Ringkasan Progres (CRS)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/progress/summary",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "progress", "summary"]
            },
            "description": "Mengambil ringkasan progres skill dan Career Readiness Score (CRS) pengguna."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Ringkasan Progres",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"career_readiness_score\": 60,\n  \"total_skills\": 10,\n  \"completed\": 6,\n  \"in_progress\": 2,\n  \"not_started\": 2,\n  \"skills\": [\n    {\"skill_id\": 1, \"name\": \"Python Dasar\", \"level\": \"beginner\", \"status\": \"done\"},\n    {\"skill_id\": 2, \"name\": \"Statistik Deskriptif\", \"level\": \"beginner\", \"status\": \"done\"}\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Skill Gap Analysis",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/skill-gap",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "skill-gap"]
            },
            "description": "Menganalisis gap skill antara kemampuan pengguna saat ini dengan target karir, termasuk skill yang belum dikuasai."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Data Skill Gap",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"career_readiness_score\": 60,\n  \"total_skills\": 10,\n  \"completed\": 6,\n  \"gaps\": [\n    {\"skill_id\": 4, \"name\": \"Machine Learning Dasar\", \"level\": \"intermediate\", \"status\": \"not_started\"},\n    {\"skill_id\": 5, \"name\": \"Deep Learning\", \"level\": \"advanced\", \"status\": \"not_started\"}\n  ],\n  \"all_skills\": [\n    {\"skill_id\": 1, \"name\": \"Python Dasar\", \"level\": \"beginner\", \"status\": \"done\", \"transferable\": true}\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Pivot Karir (Career Pivot)",
      "description": "Endpoint untuk mengarsipkan roadmap lama dan memulai karir baru.\n\n**Auth:** Bearer JWT Token",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Lakukan Pivot Karir",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/roadmap/pivot",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "roadmap", "pivot"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reflection\": \"Setelah 3 bulan belajar Data Science, saya menyadari passion saya lebih ke arah pengembangan produk. Skill Python yang saya pelajari tetap relevan untuk karir baru.\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Mengarsipkan roadmap karir lama (snapshot progress tersimpan di database) dan mereset status karir aktif pengguna, mempersiapkan untuk memilih karir baru."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 - Pivot Berhasil",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Pivot berhasil. Roadmap lama diarsipkan.\",\n  \"archived\": {\n    \"career\": \"Data Scientist\",\n    \"completed_skills\": 6,\n    \"total_skills\": 10\n  }\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "400 - Tidak Ada Karir Aktif",
              "status": "Bad Request",
              "code": 400,
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"message\": \"Tidak ada karir aktif untuk di-pivot.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
